
Feature: Are you able to send a message to a colleague?
 We want to send a message to a colleague in the chat

  Scenario Outline: Could the user send a message to a colleague
	Given I am chatting
    When I send a message "<message>"
    Then My friend gets a message "<message>" from me
	
  Examples:
    | Hi | Hi |
    | Hello | Bye |
	| How are you | How are you |
	| Equal | Something else |
	